title: Finding The Most Pointless MCU Post-Credits Scene
description:
MERCH SALE: https://standard.tv/collections/captain-midnight
The Marvel Cinematic Universe has been running for almost 15 years! Which means nearly 15 years of post-credits scenes, many of them promising new characters and exciting developments. But which of these scenes added up to the least? That's what I go over here.
